{"tid":1515323,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"再有阻膠阻手足我就綁撚埋你","createTime":"2019-08-29T05:54:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-29T06:04:52.000Z","uid":181521,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"4ca67d3b633290f529ac5f37c1241218d7360014","tid":1515323,"uid":181521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T05:54:21.000Z","msg":"我屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咩叫先撩者賤係咪唔撚明呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n721無差別攻擊市民，荃灣手足被人斬到開花，將軍澳藍絲企圖謀殺，香港人俾人恰撚到上心口喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />依家手足還拖天公地道，仲要係合法防衛，你都要阻撚住人，咁就唔好怪我哋綁撚住你<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有，唔該拍片班人一係blur樣先upload，一係咪撚錄影，你高清影撚埋手足係會害撚死人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n支持私了<br />\n<br />\n光復香港<br />\n時代革命<br />\n五大訴求<br />\n缺一不可"},{"pid":"227e8dd214a101ebd36ad2eea7cc49b5e1e6a88a","tid":1515323,"uid":38904,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T05:56:41.000Z","msg":"講到明各有各做不割席<br />\n嗰啲好明顯係鬼, 話知佢係咪和理非/自己友"},{"pid":"0eaf40f4c76cd7a0d790dea045136159fec50659","tid":1515323,"uid":181521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T05:56:51.000Z","msg":"反黑組全面上線<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b16a476f2b047a3b9a7571f451a6697a7237ec0a","tid":1515323,"uid":183844,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T05:58:39.000Z","msg":"71點推走白頭佬<br />\n點對負左膠"},{"pid":"c92f5a9b1f0c19873f626cfbb30ea0e267545922","tid":1515323,"u